FBIS4-62484 "drsov095_g_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-095 Daily Report 16 May 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Clergy Not Taking Part in Elections Clergy Not Taking Part in Elections LD1605172394 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1228 GMT 16 May 94 LD1605172394 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [Report by BELINFORM correspondent Svetlana Kalinkina -- TASS] [Text] Minsk, 16 May -- Fulfilling the decision of the Holy Synod of the Russian Orthodox Church, the Belarusian clergy will not take part in the Republic's first presidential election. A BELINFORM correspondent was informed at the office of the diocese of the Russian Orthodox Church that there is no substance in reports that the clergy are canvassing for one candidate or another or participating in groups. At the same time some church ministers have until now been actively engaging in politics; deputies at various levels are permitted to complete their term in office as set out by the law.
